title.narrative: AR CRL1 APL1 Buenos Aires Infrastructure

description.narrative: The development objectives (PDOs) of this project are to: (i) enhance the provision of water andsewerage services for the benefitof low-income people, in particular for those peopleliving in highly vulnerable areas; (ii) improve high priority road segments of theBorrower’s road network; (iii) mitigate urban flooding; and (iv) support thereactivation of the Borrower’s economy and strengthen its regional competitiveness.
